Common Table Structure (TStudent ) 

No. (Code[20]) – Primary Key 

Name (Text[100]) – Student Name 

Status (Draft, Active, Blocked) – Lifecycle state 

Is Active (Boolean) – Indicates active state 

Total Marks (Decimal) – Range 0–100 

Grade (Code[10]) – System calculated 

Email (Text[100]) – Contact email 

Phone (Text[20]) – Contact number 

Block Reason (Text[150]) – Required when blocked 

Attempt Count (Integer) – Validation failure counter 

Created By (Code[50]) – Auto-filled 

Created On (Date) – Auto-filled 

Last Modified By (Code[50]) – Auto-filled 

Last Modified On (Date) – Auto-filled 

*********************************************************

Focus: OnDeleteRecord() and Field OnValidate() 

Deletion allowed only if Status = Draft AND Total Marks = 0. 

Prevent delete if Status = Active OR Marks > 0. 

If Attempt Count ≥ 5 → Require confirmation before delete. 

Total Marks validation: 0–100 range. 

Invalid marks → increment Attempt Count. 

Marks < 40 → Auto block student. 

Marks ≥ 85 & Active → Show academic award message. 

Active status requires valid email. 

Invalid email increments Attempt Count. 

3 invalid emails → Auto block student.  

